name: "Decentral Eyes Dogg" Decentralized
description:
BeetsDAO will bid on Coldie & Snoop's "Decentral Eyes Dogg" ending on Dec 2 Superrare in partnership with Christie's. Juicebox contributors will receive $EYEZ token entitling them to mint exclusive art NFTs that hold special utility in the Metaverse.

Auction Link: https://bit.ly/3ljrEZg
payDisclosure: Holders of $EYEZ will join a vibrant community of collectors dreaming of the future of Web3. $EYEZ holders will choose derivative works to be commissioned by the community. Should the project be unsuccessful at acquiring “Decentral Eyes Dogg”, we will refund your contribution excluding gas fees and/or allow the holder to convert any portion of the $EYEZ token balance claimable in their Juicebox account.
